Description.Text: Located on an un-congested street off Kukulcan Boulevard and only a short distance from Cancun's most popular shopping and nightspots. It is a 5 minutes walk to Plaza Caracol and the Canc n Convention Center, 25 minutes by taxi to Cancun International Airport and 15 minutes by taxi to the City of Cancun

A total of 61 rooms, All studios and suites have two double beds, kitchenette with utensils, refrigerator, sink and two burner stove, individual air-conditioning, shower, telephone, color satellite T.V., marble floors and balcony.
An intimate complex of 3 buildings, each with 3 floors, that surround a courtyard and freshwater swimming pool.

The perfect complement to restful surroundings is good food and drink. . Oliver's Continental Palapa Restaurant, offers the best view in the Hotel Zone. Thecozy little open air restaurant is open daily from 7:00 A.M., serving a la carte breakfast, lunch, dinner and your favorite beverage. Cuisine prepared by Chef Oliver from a menu of continental favorites and local specialities.
